  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen we execute the attached test case (getPastLogs), the client produces the wrong values for the **logIndex** field.\r\nSimilar issues occur when using the getTransactionReceipt API.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Download test files\r\n[test_cases.zip](https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/files/9293170/test_cases.zip)\r\n\r\n2. Run the node with the following command\r\n`besu --data-path test_cases/data-besu --genesis-file test_cases/besu.json --rpc-http-port 8549 --rpc-http-enabled --rpc-http-api ETH --network-id 15 --discovery-enabled false`\r\n\r\n3. Execute the javascript test case\r\n`test1.js`\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 5, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 2, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 5, ...}\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 0, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n{ ... ,\"logIndex\": 1, ...}\r\n\r\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\r\nAlways\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: besu/v22.4.4/linux-x86_64/openjdk-java-16\r\n* OS Name & Version: Ubuntu 20.04.4 LTS\r\n",
